{"tid":750703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"贏國智庫話唔賣稀土畀美國，要餓死美國高科企業，成功左未?","createTime":"2018-07-21T06:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T14:36:31.000Z","uid":27451,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e86a1c9d5da1b09c012849dbfc67d572a7edf8c0","tid":750703,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:40:39.000Z","msg":"睇好贏國<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b88e8d659612cb974a00f45e28720616c41d012","tid":750703,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:45:03.000Z","msg":"會餓死自己先"},{"pid":"c763c6d563a5444b0ec8b9dd0acc11230645c851","tid":750703,"uid":76848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e86a1c9d5da1b09c012849dbfc67d572a7edf8c0","tid":750703,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T06:40:39.000Z","msg":"睇好贏國<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"係就好 <br />\n開採污染大 而且美國都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e778a00c29b1c12ff23b40af7fa05697a016db","tid":750703,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"其實贏國既智庫, 係唔係除左識擦鞋, 其他乜撚都唔識?"},{"pid":"cb71ba1750a8c8d2ae7696e9b25668a8cddbc1b2","tid":750703,"uid":12609,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T08:07:48.000Z","msg":"稀土是一種礦物，原來不稀有，全球很多國家也有稀土藏量。全球稀土市場每年貿易額約20億美元（約150億港元），等於長實（001）今年賣樓目標的三分之一。六十年代至八十年代，全球稀土需求大部份由一個美國稀土礦供應。即是說，稀土是一種不稀有、用量不高、價值不高的礦物。<br />\n全世界都有，點解變成由內地壟斷供應？答案是，全世界都不想開發稀土。提煉稀土過程複雜，而且對環境造成很大破壞，全球關注環保，政府不斷提升環保水平，稀土企業不斷增加環保監察成本，在西方國家，開發稀土成本越來越高。內地則漠視環保，地方政府和企業勾結，罔顧居民健康，大肆破壞環境，以低價搶爛市。例如美國的稀土出產國，敵不過「零環保成本」的內地，美國政府也樂得把生產稀土這麻煩生意，拱手讓給內地，由內地面對生產稀土製造的環保問題。內地全球稀土霸主地位，是這樣「奪」回來。人家不是沒有稀土，也不是不懂得生產，只是不想同內地爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3066cc7cf7d01434f1c7ed31b4ec4a9a94e8bf1f","tid":750703,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"餓死咗自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5ce9c529120073407980b14c6f326e7b75045d","tid":750703,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"五毛未來撚阿廢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/172928_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F172928_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1f0d78bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"63e70ef44e184caf15b045146733caa725135888","tid":750703,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c5ce9c529120073407980b14c6f326e7b75045d","tid":750703,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T09:29:31.000Z","msg":"五毛未來撚阿廢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/172928_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F172928_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=1f0d78bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T09:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/21/173006_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F21%2F173006_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=8ea2f1ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d2502132d4a9e27381359d8b1f3166f7515cd3d","tid":750703,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9e778a00c29b1c12ff23b40af7fa05697a016db","tid":750703,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"其實贏國既智庫, 係唔係除左識擦鞋, 其他乜撚都唔識?